imdb.plot outline: This show is produced and distributed by Zhejiang Television in 2017, and was hosted by five youth idols. The show sets challenges in forms of high energy games for the idols. Each episode/lesson encompasses values such as teamwork, tradition appreciation, and determination.
imdb.title: Give Me Five: Gao Neng Shao Nian Tuan
